## 3. Test Scope

### 3.1 Features In Scope

|  |  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| # | Feature / Story | Priority | FSD Reference | Test Type |
| 1 | injectAll() — Copy all CORE\_COMPONENTS + indexer | High | UC-1, BR-1, BR-2, BR-3, BR-4 | Functional, Integration |
| 2 | injectSelective() — QuickPick multi-select | High | UC-2, BR-5, BR-6, BR-7 | Functional, UI |
| 3 | copyDirRecursive() — Recursive copy with exclusions | High | UC-3, BR-8, BR-9, BR-10, BR-11 | Functional, PBT |
| 4 | copyFiltered() — Filtered copy for indexer | High | UC-4, BR-12, BR-13, BR-14, BR-15 | Functional, PBT |
| 5 | checkStatus() — Component status reporting | Medium | UC-5, BR-16, BR-17 | Functional |
| 6 | Cross-platform path handling | High | FSD Section 8 | Compatibility |
| 7 | Performance (< 5s for 500 files) | Medium | FSD Section 8 | Non-Functional |
| 8 | Error handling and notifications | High | FSD Section 9 | Functional |

